        <abstract>
            <p>Has finished arranging his pigeons’ skeletons. May consult TCE on them.</p> 
<p>CD is at work on an abstract of his conclusions on species and varieties [<hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>]. His "bigger book" [<hi rend="italic">Natural selection</hi>] will take two or three more years.</p> 
        </abstract>
